A = 
\begin{pmatrix}1 & 1& 1 & \cdots & 1 \\ 1 & 1-x & 1 & \cdots & 1 \\ 1 & 1& 2-x &\cdots & 1 \\ \cdots & \cdots & \cdots & \cdots & \cdots \\ 1& 1 & 1 &\cdots& n-1-x \end{pmatrix}
\det A=\det\begin{pmatrix}1 & 1& 1 & \cdots & 1 & 0 \\ 1 & 1-x & 1 & \cdots & 1 & 0 \\ 1 & 1& 2-x &\cdots & 1 & 0 \\ \vdots & \vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots & \vdots \\ 1& 1 & 1 &\cdots& n-2-x & 0\\1& 1 & 1 &\cdots& 1 & n-2-x \end{pmatrix}=
(n-2-x)\det\begin{pmatrix}1 & 1& 1 & \cdots & 1 \\ 1 & 1-x & 1 & \cdots & 1 \\ 1 & 1& 2-x &\cdots & 1 \\ \vdots & \vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots \\ 1& 1 & 1 & \cdots& n-2-x \end{pmatrix}.
n-2
